query:
UPDATE nest_eggs
            SET
                author = $1, name = $2, description = $3,
                config_files = $4, config_startup = $5, config_stop = $6,
                config_script = $7, startup = $8, force_outgoing_ip = $9,
                features = $10, docker_images = $11, file_denylist = $12
            WHERE nest_id = $13 AND id = $14
